    Academics' warning comes after households mixing in pubs and homes has been blamed for a rise in cases in Preston.
</p>

                

    <div class="template-article__post-info template-article__post-info--image-led ">
        
    <p class="template-article__author-name template-article__author-name--image-led template-article__author-name--image-led heading-4"  itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" >
